<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Donation Receipt — {{reference}}</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #1f2937;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 32px;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ── Header ─────────────────────────────── */
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #b45309;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .org-name {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #b45309;
    }
    .org-tagline {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-top: 4px;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .doc-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #374151;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .reference-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #fef3c7;
      color: #92400e;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: bold;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-top: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #fcd34d;
    }

    /* ── Donor Details ───────────────────────── */
    .details-section {
      background: #f9fafb;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .details-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .detail-item {}
    .detail-label {
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .detail-value {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    /* ── Amount Box ──────────────────────────── */
    .amount-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b45309, #d97706);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px 28px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .amount-label { font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.85; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    .amount-value { font-size: 40px; font-weight: bold; margin: 8px 0 4px; }
    .amount-words { font-size: 11px; opacity: 0.8; font-style: italic; }

    /* ── Gift Aid ────────────────────────────── */
    .gift-aid-box {
      border: 2px solid #16a34a;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      background: #f0fdf4;
    }
    .gift-aid-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #166534;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .gift-aid-amount {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #16a34a;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .gift-aid-text {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .gift-aid-not-eligible {
      background: #f9fafb;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    /* ── Purpose ─────────────────────────────── */
    .purpose-section {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .purpose-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .purpose-value {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #374151;
      background: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    /* ── Thank You ───────────────────────────── */
    .thankyou-section {
      border: 1px solid #fcd34d;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: #fffbeb;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .thankyou-en {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #92400e;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .thankyou-gu {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #b45309;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .thankyou-hi {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #b45309;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    .blessings {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    /* ── Footer ──────────────────────────────── */
    .footer {
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding-top: 14px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .footer-columns {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .footer-legal {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #d1d5db;
      border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
      padding-top: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="header">
    <div class="org-name">🕉 Shital Hindu Temple</div>
    <div class="org-tagline">Jay Shree Krishna — Serving the Community Since 1985</div>
    <div class="doc-title">Donation Receipt</div>
    <div class="reference-badge">Ref: {{reference}}</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Donor Details -->
  <div class="details-section">
    <div class="details-grid">
      <div class="detail-item">
        <div class="detail-label">Donor Name</div>
        <div class="detail-value">{{donorName}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-item">
        <div class="detail-label">Date of Donation</div>
        <div class="detail-value">{{donationDate}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-item">
        <div class="detail-label">Payment Method</div>
        <div class="detail-value">{{paymentMethod}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="detail-item">
        <div class="detail-label">Branch</div>
        <div class="detail-value">{{branchName}}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Donation Amount -->
  <div class="amount-box">
    <div class="amount-label">Total Donation Received</div>
    <div class="amount-value">{{currency}}{{amount}}</div>
    {{#if amountInWords}}
    <div class="amount-words">{{amountInWords}}</div>
    {{/if}}
  </div>

  <!-- Purpose -->
  <div class="purpose-section">
    <div class="purpose-label">Donation Purpose</div>
    <div class="purpose-value">{{purpose}}</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Gift Aid -->
  {{#if giftAidEligible}}
  <div class="gift-aid-box">
    <div class="gift-aid-title">&#9989; Gift Aid Declaration Confirmed</div>
    <div class="gift-aid-amount">+ {{currency}}{{giftAidAmount}} reclaimed from HMRC</div>
    <div class="gift-aid-text">
      As a UK taxpayer, your donation is eligible for Gift Aid. Shital Hindu Temple will reclaim
      25p in tax for every £1 you donate, at no extra cost to you. This means your total donation
      to the temple is worth <strong>{{currency}}{{totalWithGiftAid}}</strong>.
      <br /><br />
      Gift Aid Declaration Reference: <strong>{{giftAidDeclarationRef}}</strong>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{else}}
  <div class="gift-aid-not-eligible">
    <strong>Gift Aid:</strong> This donation is not eligible for Gift Aid, or no Gift Aid declaration
    is on file. If you are a UK taxpayer and wish to enable Gift Aid on future donations,
    please contact the temple office.
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  <!-- Thank You -->
  <div class="thankyou-section">
    <div class="thankyou-en">Thank you for your generous donation!</div>
    <div class="thankyou-gu">આપના ઉદાર દાન માટે ખૂબ ખૂબ આભાર!</div>
    <div class="thankyou-hi">आपके उदार दान के लिए हृदय से धन्यवाद!</div>
    <div class="blessings">
      Your generosity helps us serve the community and maintain our sacred temple.
      May God bless you and your family abundantly. 🙏
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <div class="footer">
    <div class="footer-columns">
      <div>
        <strong>Shital Hindu Temple</strong><br />
        Registered Charity Number: {{charityNumber}}<br />
        {{templeAddress}}<br />
        Tel: {{templePhone}} | Email: {{templeEmail}}
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:right;">
        <strong>Receipt Details</strong><br />
        Receipt No: {{reference}}<br />
        Issued: {{issuedDate}}<br />
        Issued by: {{issuedBy}}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-legal">
      This receipt is issued in accordance with the Charities Act 2011. Shital Hindu Temple is registered
      with the Charity Commission for England and Wales (Charity No. {{charityNumber}}).
      Please retain this receipt for your tax records. Gift Aid claims are made in accordance
      with HMRC regulations.
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
